{"id":240,"parent_id":238,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":240,"title":"James 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"James","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","God has chosen the poor of this world who are rich in faith—Salvation is gained by keeping the whole law—Faith without works is dead."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.1","order":"03.22.002.24879"},["b","1"],"My brethren,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"have"],"not the faith of our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Lord Jesus Christ"],",",["i","the Lord"],"of glory, with respect of persons."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.2","order":"03.22.002.24880"},["b","2"],"For if there come unto your assembly a man with a gold ring, in goodly apparel, and there come in also a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"poor"],"man in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"vile"],"raiment;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.3","order":"03.22.002.24881"},["b","3"],"And ye have respect to him that weareth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"gay"],"clothing, and say unto him, Sit thou here in a good place; and say to the poor, Stand thou there, or sit here under my footstool:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.4","order":"03.22.002.24882"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Are"],"ye not then partial in yourselves, and are become judges of evil thoughts?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.5","order":"03.22.002.24883"},["b","5"],"Hearken, my beloved brethren, Hath not God chosen the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"poor"],"of this world rich in faith, and heirs of the kingdom which he hath promised to them that love him?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.6","order":"03.22.002.24884"},["b","6"],"But ye have despised the poor. Do not rich men",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"oppress"],"you, and draw you before the judgment seats?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.7","order":"03.22.002.24885"},["b","7"],"Do not they blaspheme that worthy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"name"],"by the which ye are called?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.8","order":"03.22.002.24886"},["b","8"],"If ye fulfil the royal law according to the scripture, Thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"love"],"thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"neighbour"],"as thyself, ye do well:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.9","order":"03.22.002.24887"},["b","9"],"But if ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"respect"],"to persons, ye commit sin, and are convinced of the law as transgressors."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.10","order":"03.22.002.24888"},["b","10"],"For whosoever shall keep the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"whole"],"law, and yet",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"offend"],"in one",["i","point,"],"he is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"guilty"],"of all."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.11","order":"03.22.002.24889"},["b","11"],"For he that said, Do not commit",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"adultery"],", said also, Do not kill. Now if thou commit no adultery, yet if thou kill, thou art become a transgressor of the law."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.12","order":"03.22.002.24890"},["b","12"],"So speak ye, and so do, as they that shall be judged by the law of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"liberty"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.13","order":"03.22.002.24891"},["b","13"],"For he shall have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"judgment"],"without",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"mercy"],", that hath shewed no mercy; and mercy rejoiceth against judgment."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.14","order":"03.22.002.24892"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"What"],["i","doth it"],"profit, my brethren, though a man say he hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"faith"],", and have not works? can faith save him?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.15","order":"03.22.002.24893"},["b","15"],"If a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"brother"],"or sister be naked, and destitute of daily",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"food"],","],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.16","order":"03.22.002.24894"},["b","16"],"And one of you say unto them, Depart in peace, be",["i","ye"],"warmed and filled; notwithstanding ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"give"],"them not those things which are needful to the body; what",["i","doth it"],"profit?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.17","order":"03.22.002.24895"},["b","17"],"Even so",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"faith"],", if it hath not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"works"],", is dead, being alone."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.18","order":"03.22.002.24896"},["b","18"],"Yea, a man may say, Thou hast faith, and I have works: shew me thy faith without thy works, and I will shew thee my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"faith"],"by my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"works"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.19","order":"03.22.002.24897"},["b","19"],"Thou believest that there is one God; thou doest well: the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"devils"],"also",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"believe"],", and tremble."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.20","order":"03.22.002.24898"},["b","20"],"But wilt thou know, O vain man, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"faith"],"without",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"works"],"is dead?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.21","order":"03.22.002.24899"},["b","21"],"Was not Abraham our father",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"justified"],"by works, when he had",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"offered"],"Isaac his son upon the altar?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.22","order":"03.22.002.24900"},["b","22"],"Seest thou how faith wrought with his works, and by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"works"],"was faith made",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"perfect"],"?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.23","order":"03.22.002.24901"},["b","23"],"And the scripture was fulfilled which saith, Abraham",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"believed"],"God, and it was imputed unto him for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"righteousness"],": and he was called the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"Friend"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.24","order":"03.22.002.24902"},["b","24"],"Ye see then how that by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"works"],"a man is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"justified"],", and not by faith only."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.25","order":"03.22.002.24903"},["b","25"],"Likewise also was not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Rahab"],"the harlot",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"justified"],"by works, when she had received the messengers, and had sent",["i","them"],"out another way?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.26","order":"03.22.002.24904"},["b","26"],"For as the body without the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"spirit"],"is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"dead"],", so faith without",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"works"],"is dead also."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.1a","order":"03.22.002.24905"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"not with partiality, have the faith of our Lord.",["span.small","JST"],"James 2:1 …",["i","ye cannot"],"have the faith of our Lord Jesus Christ, the Lord of glory,",["i","and yet have"],"respect",["i","to"],"persons."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.1b","order":"03.22.002.24907"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lord"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.2a","order":"03.22.002.24909"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.2b","order":"03.22.002.24911"},["b","2b"],["span.small","GR"],"dirty."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.3a","order":"03.22.002.24913"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"splendid."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.4a","order":"03.22.002.24915"},["b","4a"],["span.small","JST"],"James 2:4 Are ye not then in yourselves",["i","partial judges,"],"and become evil",["i","in your"],"thoughts?"],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.5a","order":"03.22.002.24917"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/15.16"},"Prov. 15:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.3"},"Matt. 5:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.20"},"Luke 6:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.27.27-28"},"1 Cor. 1:27 (27–28)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.6a","order":"03.22.002.24919"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/oppression"},"TG Oppression"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.7a","order":"03.22.002.24921"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.8a","order":"03.22.002.24923"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.8b","order":"03.22.002.24925"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/neighbor"},"TG Neighbor"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.9a","order":"03.22.002.24927"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/1.17"},"Deut. 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/28.21"},"Prov. 28:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.10a","order":"03.22.002.24929"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.28.28-29"},"D&C 50:28 (28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.10b","order":"03.22.002.24931"},["b","10b"],["span.small","GR"],"stumble, err.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/offense"},"TG Offense"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.10c","order":"03.22.002.24933"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guilt"},"TG Guilt"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.11a","order":"03.22.002.24935"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.12a","order":"03.22.002.24937"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/liberty"},"TG Liberty"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.13a","order":"03.22.002.24939"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.7"},"Ps. 109:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.13b","order":"03.22.002.24941"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mercy"},"TG Mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.14a","order":"03.22.002.24943"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-james/2.14-21"},["span.small","JST"],"James 2:14–21 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.14b","order":"03.22.002.24945"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.69"},"D&C 20:69"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.15a","order":"03.22.002.24947"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.15b","order":"03.22.002.24949"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/food"},"TG Food"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.16a","order":"03.22.002.24951"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/3.11.8-14"},"Luke 3:11 (8–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.18"},"D&C 104:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.17a","order":"03.22.002.24953"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.3"},"1 Thes. 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.17b","order":"03.22.002.24955"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"TG Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.18a","order":"03.22.002.24957"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.18b","order":"03.22.002.24959"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.20.15-20"},"Matt. 7:20 (15–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.37"},"D&C 20:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.19a","order":"03.22.002.24961"},["b","19a"],["span.small","JST"],"James 2:19 … devils also believe, and tremble;",["i","thou hast made thyself like unto them, not being justified."],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/16.17"},"Acts 16:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.19b","order":"03.22.002.24963"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/8.28.27-28"},"Luke 8:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.20a","order":"03.22.002.24965"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.20b","order":"03.22.002.24967"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/24.12"},"Prov. 24:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.21a","order":"03.22.002.24969"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.17"},"Heb. 11:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.21b","order":"03.22.002.24971"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/22.9.9-12"},"Gen. 22:9 (9–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.22a","order":"03.22.002.24973"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.22b","order":"03.22.002.24975"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"TG Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.23a","order":"03.22.002.24977"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/22.12"},"Gen. 22:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.23b","order":"03.22.002.24979"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.23c","order":"03.22.002.24981"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/41.8"},"Isa. 41:8"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/friendship"},"TG Friendship"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.24a","order":"03.22.002.24983"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.23"},"2 Ne. 25:23"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.24b","order":"03.22.002.24985"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justification"},"TG Justification"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.25a","order":"03.22.002.24987"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/2.1"},"Josh. 2:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.25b","order":"03.22.002.24989"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.31"},"Heb. 11:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.26a","order":"03.22.002.24991"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirit-body"},"TG Spirit Body"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-disembodied"},"Spirits, Disembodied"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.26b","order":"03.22.002.24993"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death"},"TG Death"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.26c","order":"03.22.002.24995"},["b","26c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."]]}
